sources.title: Jesse James at Bay
sources.description: Jesse James' double is pillaging the countryside.

sources.title: Jesse James at Bay  (1941) ROY ROGERS
sources.description:
Stars: Roy Rogers, George 'Gabby' Hayes, Sally Payne
Director: Joseph Kane

Jesse James joins with Missouri settlers in their battle with rich, land-grabbing railroad tycoons.

metadata.Plot: When Jesse learns that Krager is cheating settlers, he and his gang rob trains to obtain money for them to purchase their land. Krager, finding a Jesse look alike in Burns, hires him to wreak havoc on the ranchers. When Jesse kills Burns he switches clothes and goes after the culprits.
metadata.Actors: Roy Rogers, George 'Gabby' Hayes, Sally Payne
